title: [FSX/P3D] Orbx FTX: NA KJAC Jackson Hole Airport v1.10
description:
Orbx FTX: NA KJAC Jackson Hole Airport v1.10
[Latest quad installer for FSX / P3D / P3Dv2 / P3Dv3]

This is an Orbx FTX airport, and as such a copy of Orbx FTX NA Gold USA Central Rocky Mountains must be installed prior to use.


NOTE: there was an error on Orbx website claiming the KJAC for P3Dv3 (Quad Installer) is v1.15 when in fact the installer itself indicates v1.10.
this shouldn't really matter to you as this is the latest Installer for KJAC that was released, as of 27/12/15
